Custom Views and View Groups
    - Extending existing widgets (views)
        - Extend the widgets class
        - Implement customizations
    - Create a custom view from scratch
        - Extend the view class
        - Override 2 Methods
            - onDraw
                - Paint the to a canvas
            -onMeasure
                - Adjustments and other considerations for parent layout
                        size
    - Custom View Groups (Compound Views)
        - Extend the ViewGroup class desired (LinearLayout, Constraint, ...)
        - override the onLayout Method
            - Dictate positions of child views
